title: Places I've Visited in the Last Year
name: Places I've Visited in the Last Year

properties.name: Chicago
properties.description: Posted by NyoustChicago, ILChicago was the site of my first school trip at University of Tennessee. We went in fall semester 2006. We looked around the city, had tours, and were able to freely roam (as long as we were with someone). Long bus ride back which finally got us back to UT around 5 in the morning. I was awake the entire time.

properties.name: Hilton Head Island
properties.description: Posted by NyoustHilton Head Island, SCMy older brother lives in Hilton Head Island with his girlfriend. I have visited a few time over the summer as well as during my Spring Break, spring semester 2007.

properties.name: Home
properties.description: Posted by NyoustNewark, DEThis is my permanent city of residence. I have lived here since about 1992, I was almost 5 years old when we moved.

properties.name: Kenna
properties.description: Posted by NyoustKenna, WVMy room mate of three years lives in this city. I visited over the summer and had my first experience shooting a gun as well as going to the Dog Tracks.

properties.name: Myrtle Beach
properties.description: Posted by Nyoust  Myrtle Beach, SCI have been to Myrtle Beach during my Spring Break in spring semester 2007. There I stayed at a friends grandmother\'s house while my friend and I explored the city. it was part of an arrangement where we visited my older brother for half the week and than we visited her grandmother the second half of the week.

properties.name: New York City
properties.description: Posted by NyoustNew York City, NYI visited New York City as part of a school project. We went to look the different buildings around the city before we went to Princeton University, which was the site of our recent project.

properties.name: Ocean City
properties.description: Posted by NyoustOcean City, MDOcean City has been a tradition almost every summer since I\'ve been about 8 years old. Over the summer wasn\'t any different. A group of my cousin\'s and my own friends come together to stay in a beach house almost literally on the beach.

properties.name: Philadelphia
properties.description: Posted by NyoustPhiladelphia, PAI\'ve visited Philadelphia with one of my friends over the summer. We went to the Philadelphia Museum of Art.

properties.name: Radford University
properties.description: Posted by NyoustRadford, VAMy younger brother and a few friends go to school here. I have visited him to help move him in. I have also been there to pick him up and watch Boomsday with me in Knoxville. The most recent trip was a break from driving on my way back to Knoxville from home.

properties.name: Schenectady
properties.description: Posted by NyoustSchanectady, NYMy cousins on my father\'s side live here. I recently visited because one of my cousins was getting married. I attended as a groomsmen.

properties.name: Univercity of Cincinnati
properties.description: Posted by NyoustCincinnati, OHThe University of Cincinnati was a stop we made on another school trip, fall semester 2006. We looked at the buildings across the university, but most specifically we were told to visit the Architecture building while we were there. A few friends and I believe the building\'s elevator tried to kill us after what felt like dropping a few floors and than staying closed for what seemed like a very long time.

properties.name: University of Tennessee
properties.description: Posted by NyoustKnoxville, TNThis is the place I go to school. My major is architecture.

properties.name: West Virginia University
properties.description: Posted by NyoustMorgantown, WVOne of the friends who I met in Knoxville goes to school at WVU now. I visited over the summer right before she took me to visit another friend in Kenna. The most recent trip was over my Fall Break where I went for a visit and to hang out.
